include ../config/config
block config
doctype html
html(lang='es')

  head

    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
    meta(name='description', content='')
    meta(name='author', content='')

    title #{siteName}

    // Favicon
    link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')

    // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
    link(href='css/app.css', rel='stylesheet')

  body

    // Responsive navbar
    nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.bg-dark
      .container.px-5
        a.navbar-brand(href='#!') #{siteName}
        button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarSupportedContent', aria-controls='navbarSupportedContent', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
          span.navbar-toggler-icon
        #navbarSupportedContent.collapse.navbar-collapse
          ul.navbar-nav.ms-auto.mb-2.mb-lg-0
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.active(aria-current='page', href='#!') Home
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='#!') About
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='#!') Contact
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='#!') Services

    // Header
    header.bg-dark.py-5
      .container.px-5
        .row.gx-5.justify-content-center
          .col-lg-6
            .text-center.my-5
              h1.display-5.fw-bolder.text-white.mb-2 Todo lo que necesitas para compartir tu contenido
              p.lead.text-white-50.mb-4 #{siteName} es la mejor herramienta para compartir textos, enlaces, imágenes y videos de manera fácil, rápida y sencilla. Comienza Ahora es GRATIS!
              .d-grid.gap-3.d-sm-flex.justify-content-sm-center
                a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.px-4.me-sm-3(href='#features') Registro
                a.btn.btn-outline-light.btn-lg.px-4(href='#!') Inicio sesión

    // Features section
    section#features.py-5.border-bottom
      .container.px-5.my-5
        .row.gx-5
          .col
            .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-3
              i.fa.fa-file
            h2.h4.fw-bolder Crea
            p
              | Contamos con varias herramientas para personalizar tus pastes de manera rápida y creativa.
          .col
            .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-3
              i.fa.fa-building
            h2.h4.fw-bolder Protege
            p
              | Protege tus pastes con captcha y contraseña, los robots no podrán ver tus publicaciones.
          .col
            .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-3
              i.fa.fa-file
            h2.h4.fw-bolder Acorta y gana
            p
              | Acorta Fácil y Rápidamente tus enlaces y gana dinero con el acortador de tu preferencia, además podrás cambiarlo cuando quieras de manera automática sin tener que cambiar todos tus enlaces manualmente.
          .col
            .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-3
              i.fa.fa-file
            h2.h4.fw-bolder Comparte
            p
              | Comparte textos, enlaces y haz que lleguen a todo el mundo de una manera segura y eficaz.


    // Pricing section
    section.bg-light.py-5.border-bottom
      .container.px-5.my-5
        .text-center.mb-5
          h2.fw-bolder Pay as you grow
          p.lead.mb-0 With our no hassle pricing plans
        .row.gx-5.justify-content-center
          // Pricing card free
          .col-lg-6.col-xl-4
            .card.mb-5.mb-xl-0
              .card-body.p-5
                .small.text-uppercase.fw-bold.text-muted Free
                .mb-3
                  span.display-4.fw-bold $0
                  span.text-muted / mo.
                ul.list-unstyled.mb-4
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    strong 1 users
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | 5GB storage
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | Unlimited public projects
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | Community access
                  li.mb-2.text-muted
                    i.fa.fa-x
                    | Unlimited private projects
                  li.mb-2.text-muted
                    i.fa.fa-x
                    | Dedicated support
                  li.mb-2.text-muted
                    i.fa.fa-x
                    | Free linked domain
                  li.text-muted
                    i.fa.fa-x
                    | Monthly status reports
                .d-grid
                  a.btn.btn-outline-primary(href='#!') Choose plan
          // Pricing card pro
          .col-lg-6.col-xl-4
            .card.mb-5.mb-xl-0
              .card-body.p-5
                .small.text-uppercase.fw-bold
                  i.fa.fa-star-fill.text-warning
                  | Pro
                .mb-3
                  span.display-4.fw-bold $9
                  span.text-muted / mo.
                ul.list-unstyled.mb-4
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    strong 5 users
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | 5GB storage
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | Unlimited public projects
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | Community access
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | Unlimited private projects
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | Dedicated support
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | Free linked domain
                  li.text-muted
                    i.fa.fa-x
                    | Monthly status reports
                .d-grid
                  a.btn.btn-primary(href='#!') Choose plan
          // Pricing card enterprise
          .col-lg-6.col-xl-4
            .card
              .card-body.p-5
                .small.text-uppercase.fw-bold.text-muted Enterprise
                .mb-3
                  span.display-4.fw-bold $49
                  span.text-muted / mo.
                ul.list-unstyled.mb-4
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    strong Unlimited users
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | 5GB storage
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | Unlimited public projects
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | Community access
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | Unlimited private projects
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | Dedicated support
                  li.mb-2
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    strong Unlimited
                    | linked domains
                  li.text-muted
                    i.fa.fa-check.text-primary
                    | Monthly status reports
                .d-grid
                  a.btn.btn-outline-primary(href='#!') Choose plan

    // Testimonials section
    section.py-5.border-bottom
      .container.px-5.my-5.px-5
        .text-center.mb-5
          h2.fw-bolder Customer testimonials
          p.lead.mb-0 Our customers love working with us
        .row.gx-5.justify-content-center
          .col-lg-6
            // Testimonial 1
            .card.mb-4
              .card-body.p-4
                .d-flex
                  .flex-shrink-0
                    i.fa.fa-home.text-primary.fs-1
                  .ms-4
                    p.mb-1 Thank you for putting together such a great product. We loved working with you and the whole team, and we will be recommending you to others!
                    .small.text-muted - Client Name, Location
            // Testimonial 2
            .card
              .card-body.p-4
                .d-flex
                  .flex-shrink-0
                    i.fa.fa-home.text-primary.fs-1
                  .ms-4
                    p.mb-1 The whole team was a huge help with putting things together for our company and brand. We will be hiring them again in the near future for additional work!
                    .small.text-muted - Client Name, Location

    // Contact section
    section.bg-light.py-5
      .container.px-5.my-5.px-5
        .text-center.mb-5
          .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-3
            i.fa.fa-envelope
          h2.fw-bolder Contáctanos 
          p.lead.mb-0 responderemos lo mas rápido posible
        .row.gx-5.justify-content-center
          .col-lg-6

            form#contactForm(data-sb-form-api-token='API_TOKEN')

              // Name input
              .form-floating.mb-3
                input#name.form-control(
                  type='text',
                  placeholder='Enter your name...'
                  data-sb-validations='required'
                )
                label(for='name') Full name
                .invalid-feedback(data-sb-feedback='name:required')
                  | A name is required.

              // Email address input
              .form-floating.mb-3
                input#email.form-control(
                  type='email',
                  placeholder='name@example.com'
                  data-sb-validations='required,email'
                )
                label(for='email') Email address
                .invalid-feedback(data-sb-feedback='email:required')
                  | An email is required.
                .invalid-feedback(data-sb-feedback='email:email')
                  | Email is not valid.

              // Phone number input
              .form-floating.mb-3
                input#phone.form-control(
                  type='tel',
                  placeholder='(123) 456-7890'
                  data-sb-validations='required'
                )
                label(for='phone') Phone number
                .invalid-feedback(data-sb-feedback='phone:required')
                  | A phone number is required.

              // Message input
              .form-floating.mb-3
                textarea#message.form-control(
                  type='text',
                  placeholder='Enter your message here...',
                  style='height: 10rem;'
                  data-sb-validations='required'
                )
                label(for='message') Message
                .invalid-feedback(data-sb-feedback='message:required')
                  | A message is required.

              // Submit success message
              //
              // This is what your users will see when the form
              // has successfully submitted
              #submitSuccessMessage.d-none
                .text-center.mb-3
                  .fw-bolder Form submission successful!
                  | To activate this form, sign up at
                  br
                  a(href='https://startbootstrap.com/solution/contact-forms') https://startbootstrap.com/solution/contact-forms

              // Submit error message
              //
              // This is what your users will see when there is
              // an error submitting the form
              #submitErrorMessage.d-none
                .text-center.text-danger.mb-3 Error sending message!

              // Submit Button
              .d-grid
                button#submitButton.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.disabled(type='submit') Submit

    // Footer
    footer.py-5.bg-dark
      .container.px-5
        p.m-0.text-center.text-white Copyright &copy; #{siteName} 2022

    // Bootstrap core JS
    script(src='js/app.js')